The paper discusses program analysis, which is a subfield of programming languages (cs.PL). Additionally, the paper proposes a new approach to program analysis, which may be of interest to the subfield of software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also mentions approximations, which are commonly used in formal methods (cs.FL) and cryptography (cs.CR).
